data.description: Welcome home to this beauty in the very much desired Heather Ridge neighborhood.  As you enter the front door you are greeted by the large formal dining room with trayed ceilings on the left, on the right you will find the den/office complete with custom bookshelves.  Straight ahead you will find the beautiful kitchen with a large custom island, living room, and the beautiful family room addition complete with a stone fireplace.  Upstairs you will find the 4 bedrooms and 2 full baths.  All of this on a large lot with a private back yard.  50 Year warranty metal roof.
